Multi-hand is an offensive skill that enables the player character to use
two handed weapons without incurring a penalty Players without this skill 
do poorer in combat when using two handed weapons. It is a good skill
to have in combination with milt-weapon. Players who wish to play a 
swashbuckling type character archetype might want to choose this skill. 
The higher the skill level the more damage you will inflict on your
opponents.
